Package syntax

package syntax
This package provides classes that are responsible for building, parsing and representation of term syntax tree
  • Class
    Description
    Constant
    A representation of a constant term
    FunctionalSymbolFirstTermIterator
    This class provides an ability to iterate over nodes in the syntax tree.
    PreOrderTermIterator
    This class provides an ability to iterate over nodes in the syntax tree.
    Term
    A node of first-order term syntax tree.
    TermDagParser
    This class provides methods to create directed acyclic graph representation of the provided first-order term.
    TermPair
    A pair of terms with shared variables.
    TermParser
    This class provides methods to create syntax tree of the provided first-order term.
    TermWithArgs
    A representation of a term consisting of a functional symbol of non-zero arity and a list of child terms.
    Token
    A record class to store token data.
    Token.Type
    Defines token type.
    TokenIterator
    This iterator allows to tokenize provided character sequence and traverse through tokens.
    Variable
    A representation of a variable term
